Essence of this App

## Backend
# We are using mongogb and mongoose as an ODM. Storing data on mongogb Atlas.
# Generated JWT secret key via bash terminal using: openssl rand -base 64 32
# Added middleware for authentication and autherization

## Frontend
# Used Daisy UI and Taildwind CSS Glassmorphism effect
# Used Zustand -> for state management
# Used socket.io for real time communication

